(88, 96, 'Super water charger (Every drop of medicine makes it valuable) Super water charger Made by Indian technology, ', '1-5', 'DP', 'good', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Super water charger (Every drop of medicine makes it valuable) Super water charger Made by Indian technology, 1) Silicone base 3) Based on nanotechnology 1) 100% organic and petented obtained 3) seven in one benefits in 21 st century advanced sprader. Super water Charger are job seven in one works . Super faster spreader. (Spreads fast), Super Deeper Penetrator. (Deeply absorbed), super shine activator. (Activates brilliantly), opens stomata, super solid mixer. (Blends seamlessly), Super Fine Weter (Soaking Barley), Super Helper adguent. (Effectiveness), super growth promoter (satisfies the need for stimulants and silicone) It provides more effective results by reducing farmers&#39; weedicide, pesticides, fungicides and nutrients by 30%. It supplies organic silicone to the crop, thus protecting the crop from soil and crop fungus. Every time spraying chemical or organic pesticides, fungicides, nutrients and fertilizers and weeds should be used together. Irrigate the soil with&nbsp; water&nbsp; charger when water is scarce and the crop is deficient in silicon.</span></span></strong></p>\n', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Ratio:-</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> Spraying 0.1 ml per liter of water / drip: 50 to 100 ml per acre with the medicine and increasing the effect of the drug.&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span