(89, 102, 'Super Fungi Cleaner It is an internationally-classed organic broad spectrum fungicidal fertilizer. The natural phosphorus available in Super Fungi Cleaner is immediately activated and its antifungal properties reflect various types of fungal diseases. ', '1-5', 'DA', 'good', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Super Fungi Cleaner It is an internationally-classed organic broad spectrum fungicidal fertilizer. The natural phosphorus available in Super Fungi Cleaner is immediately activated and its antifungal properties reflect various types of fungal diseases. Eg. phyto and late blight, arthroconnose, downy mildew, altenaria and early blight, petal blight, root rot and others. The Organic Potassium Molecule Powder in Super Fungi Cleaner is a highly effective&nbsp; on mildew and works to stop (kuj). Potassium is a regulator of various enzymes. E.g. Secretion of salicylic acid, which acts as a fungus resistance hormone. Therefore, an additional benefit of increasing the immunity of crops is that the organic phosphorus and potash in Super Fungi Clear nourishes the crop as an excellent fertilizer which improves the size and quality of the fruits. Regular use of it will yield good results. Spraying on the ground during the cultivation of the crop will help to destroy roots of the fungus. Whenever there is an infection of oily spot, blight, fungus and powdery, spray them regularly.</span></span></strong></p>\n', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Ratio:-</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"> 1-2 grams per liter spray</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif